Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of data augmentation and deep learning techniques, which are related to machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also mentions the use of multiple datasets, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for person re-ID, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
